{"tid":1694404,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"C.朗慰問高美斯：早日康復 歸來會變得更強大","createTime":"2019-11-05T06:49:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T04:15:14.000Z","uid":173952,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1cd2135afa01d622a1709e3a8c0b68b9d731ed5a","tid":1694404,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T06:49:08.000Z","msg":"11月4日淩晨進行的熱刺與愛華頓的比賽中，孫興慜（Son Heung-Min）放鏟導致高美斯（Andre Gomes）意外重傷。對此，C.朗拿度在Instagram曬出了自己與高美斯在國家隊的照片，同時祈禱高美斯早日康復，並表示高美斯歸來後「將變得更加強大」。<br />\n<br />\n  11月4日晚，愛華頓官方發佈公告，淩晨比賽中嚴重受傷的安達-高美斯成功接受手術，以修復踝關節骨折錯位，手術進行得十分順利。"},{"pid":"72d3af6b53ecd814ae8fbe5c1be6d0b81028ac21","tid":1694404,"uid":103914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T06:55:07.000Z","msg":"C.朗拿度在Instagram曬出了自己與高美斯在國家隊的照片?<br />\n<br />\n冇喎"},{"pid":"3743648a05416d82104b5958759951e03622c0f5","tid":1694404,"uid":199081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72d3af6b53ecd814ae8fbe5c1be6d0b81028ac21","tid":1694404,"uid":103914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T06:55:07.000Z","msg":"C.朗拿度在Instagram曬出了自己與高美斯在國家隊的照片?<br />\n<br />\n冇喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T06:59:05.000Z","msg":"story"},{"pid":"63472a2e0fe196d0ac44b8d03b7eb2f42b0e4485","tid":1694404,"uid":163193,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T07:02:23.000Z","msg":"圖<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yv6gEJE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyv6gEJE.png&h=a6a2ca31&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e45aa7173ec71d026c4ea51b9fd6b0d54b34e779","tid":1694404,"uid":65298,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T07:04:18.000Z","msg":"睇錯 C.朗慰問美斯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"946861bd3083c53ac34a67f4110a422a7194f89c","tid":1694404,"uid":297508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e45aa7173ec71d026c4ea51b9fd6b0d54b34e779","tid":1694404,"uid":65298,"like":8,"dislike":0,